@ZUMA.API_HostAddress = http://localhost:5044
@ApiVersion = v1

### Version 1.0 - Get User by ID
GET {{ZUMA.API_HostAddress}}/api/{{ApiVersion}}/user/1
Accept: application/json

###

### Version 1.0 - Get All Users
GET {{ZUMA.API_HostAddress}}/api/{{ApiVersion}}/user
Accept: application/json

###

### Version 2.0 - Get All Users (Paged)
GET {{ZUMA.API_HostAddress}}/api/v2/user?page=1&pageSize=10
Accept: application/json

###

### Version 1.0 - Create User
POST {{ZUMA.API_HostAddress}}/api/{{ApiVersion}}/user
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "John Doe",
  "email": "john@example.com",
  "userName": "johndoe",
  "PASS": "SecurePASS123!"
}

###

### Version 2.0 - Create User (Enhanced)
POST {{ZUMA.API_HostAddress}}/api/v2/user
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Jane Doe",
  "email": "jane@example.com",
  "userName": "janedoe",
  "PASS": "SecurePASS123!"
}

###

### Version 1.0 - Update User
PUT {{ZUMA.API_HostAddress}}/api/{{ApiVersion}}/user/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Jane Doe",
  "email": "jane@example.com",
  "userName": "janedoe",
  "PASS": "NewPASS123!"
}

###

### Version 2.0 - Update User
PUT {{ZUMA.API_HostAddress}}/api/v2/user/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Jane Doe Updated",
  "email": "jane.updated@example.com",
  "userName": "janedoe",
  "PASS": "NewPASS123!"
}

###

### Version 1.0 & 2.0 - Delete User
DELETE {{ZUMA.API_HostAddress}}/api/{{ApiVersion}}/user/1
Accept: application/json